H0.text: Rotation is the term that describes the path the Moon travels around Earth.

H1.text: Day is the term that describes the path the Moon travels around Earth.

H2.text: Orbit is the term that describes the path the Moon travels around Earth.

H3.text: Phase is the term that describes the path the Moon travels around Earth.

A4.text: orbit refers to a regularly repeating trajectory, although it may also refer to a non-repeating trajectory.
